tion%20I%20chose%20is%20five%20houses%20that%20are%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftuscany-americans-moving-italy-cost-of-living-slow-pace-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETuscany%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20South%20of%20France%2C%20the%20French%20Alps%2C%20the%20Cotswolds%20in%20England%2C%20and%20Mallorca.%20The%20three%20tiers%20are%20small%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20large%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20in%20the%20small%2C%20which%20is%20three%20to%20four%20bedrooms%20per%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20buy-in%20was%20360%2C000%20euros%20(or%20%24394%2C117)%2C%20and%20that's%20a%20flat%20one-time%20fee.%20There's%20an%20annual%20fee%20that%20includes%20maintenance%2C%20electrical%2C%20and%20taxes%20as%20well%2C%20and%20that's%20about%20%2410%2C000%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESpending%20time%20abroad%20has%20always%20appealed%20to%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20toyed%20or%20flirted%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20living%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Colgate%20University%2C%20in%20upstate%20New%20York.%20I%20took%20a%20semester%20and%20lived%20in%20Stockholm%20and%20I%20loved%20that%20experience.%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%2C%20especially%20Americans%2C%20go%20to%20Europe%2C%20and%20every%20four%20days%20they're%20in%20another%20city%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20many%20places%20can%20I%20cross%20off%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20the%20opposite%2C%20and%20I%20stayed%20put.%20I%20just%20loved%20feeling%20settled%20and%20familiar.%20I%20used%20the%20subway%20system.%20I%20got%20shockingly%20good%20at%20reading%20and%20speaking%20Swedish%20%E2%80%94%20none%20of%20which%20I%20could%20do%20now%20%E2%80%94%20but%20I%20really%20loved%20that%20sense%20of%20place%20and%20home%20that%20I%20felt%20after%20being%20there%20for%20just%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20graduated%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20job%20opportunities%20abroad%2C%20but%20it%20was%20just%20never%20the%20right%20thing.%20It%20never%20presented%20itself%2C%20so%20I%20was%20never%20able%20to%20move%20fully%20abroad.%20But%20that%20dream%20has%20always%20been%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20exterior%20of%20a%20house%20in%20Mallorca%2C%20Spain.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea3a51ce7f1785b2e7a736%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221642%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAugust%20Collections'%20Mallorca%2C%20Spain%2C%20property.%3Cp%3EAugust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20pandemic%2C%20when%20the%20realities%20of%20what%20work%20looked%20like%20completely%20shifted%20for%20many%20people%2C%20that%20opened%20up%20the%20possibility.%20Maybe%20this%20is%20something%20I%20could%20do%20sooner%20than%20I%20thought.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20think%20we'd%20be%20having%20this%20conversation%20if%20it%20weren't%20for%20the%20pandemic.%20If%20nothing%20had%20changed%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20work%20remotely%2C%20I'm%20not%20sure%20this%20would've%20happened%20for%20me%20at%20this%20point%20in%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20very%20enamored%20with%20travel%20and%20living%20abroad%20potentially%2C%20or%20at%20least%20spending%20a%20good%20chunk%20of%20time%20away%20from%20my%20home%20base.%20It%20happened%20sooner%20than%20I%20ever%20expected%2C%20but%20it%20was%20something%20that%20I've%20thought%20about%20even%20since%20high%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPart-owning%20the%20vacation%20homes%20is%20a%20blast%20so%20far%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2021%20families%20that%20have%20access.%20So%20I%20own%201%2F21st%20of%20this%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20get%20that%20type%20of%20familiarity%20and%20ties%20to%20a%20place%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20hassle%20of%20having%20to%20have%20a%20property%20manager%2C%20or%20the%20roof's%20leaking%20but%20I'm%204%2C000%20miles%20away.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20stress%20and%20responsibility%20when%20you%20get%20to%20the%20house.%20There%20are%20none%20of%20the%20logistical%20burdens%20that%20come%20with%20homeownership.%20I'm%20a%20renter%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20so%20much%20I%20don't%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20an%20atypical%20August%20buyer.%20Most%20people%20are%20European%2C%20are%20older%20with%20kids%20who%20are%20at%20least%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20or%20they're%20retired.%20I%20am%20a%20big%20outlier%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20and%20that%20works%20perfectly%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAugust%20breaks%20it%20down%20by%20points.%20Everyone%20gets%20the%20same%20amount%20of%20points%2C%20so%20it's%20very%20egalitarian.%20You%20get%2036%20points%20a%20year%2C%20and%20each%20week%20is%20weighted%20differently.%20Peak%20summer%20months%20are%20five%20points%2C%20and%20then%20shoulder-season%20weeks%20are%20two%20points.%20It%20kind%20of%20fluctuates%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20this%20was%20also%20a%20really%20attractive%20point%3A%20I%20have%20the%20flexibility%20of%20being%20able%20to%20use%20the%20lower-point%20weeks%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20kids%20in%20school.%20Do%20I%20want%20to%20go%20for%20a%20month%20in%20October%3F%20I%20could%20do%20that%2C%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20someone%20else's%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20south%20of%20France%20next%20month%20with%20my%20parents.%20In%20the%20fall%2C%20I'm%20going%20on%20a%20trip%20with%20some%20of%20my%20girlfriends%20from%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlways%20having%20something%20to%20look%20forward%20to%20feels%20really%20good.%20Really%2C%20really%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFractional%20ownership%20worked%20for%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20no%20world%20could%20I%20buy%20something%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20in%20a%20place%20I%20was%20happy%20with%2C%20for%20that%20amount%20of%20money.%20That%20money%20is%20going%20nowhere%20where%20I%20live.%20But%20370%2C000%20euros%2C%20which%20includes%20one%20year's%20annual%20fee%2C%20can%20go%20fairly%20far%20in%20some%20of%20these%20places%20%E2%80%94%20in%20Tuscany%2C%20or%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-to-france-from-usa-buying-house-leaving-texas-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cost%20perspective%2C%20it%20became%20a%20no-brainer.%20The%20cost%20went%20so%20much%20farther%20here.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20house%20in%20Tuscany%2C%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea39956080194819fdd461%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221626%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAugust%20Collections'%20Tuscany%20property.%3Cp%3EAugust.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20the%20portfolio%20is%20worth%207%20million%20euros%20(or%20%247%2C655%2C025).%20I%20don't%20have%207%20million%20euros%20to%20buy%20five%20properties%20across%20Europe.%20So%20what%20I%20got%20access%20to%20was%20so%20much%20greater%20than%20anything%20I%20would've%20been%20able%20to%20achieve%20on%20my%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20never%20no%20risk%20associated%20with%20purchasing%20or%20investing%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20but%20there%20are%20certainly%20safer%20locations%20to%20invest%20in.%20I%20felt%20pretty%20confident%20that%20the%20public%20at%20large%2C%20who%20would%20be%20interested%20in%20these%20properties%2C%20aren't%20going%20to%20wake%20up%20one%20morning%20and%20decide%20that%20they%20don't%20like%20Tuscany%20anymore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20established%2C%20sought-after%20locations%20that%20will%20always%20have%20an%20appeal%20to%20a%20certain%20demographic.%20So%20I%20also%20felt%20safe%20in%20that%20regard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20the%20joys%20of%20homeownership%20but%20none%20of%20the%20stress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20is%20my%20home%2C%20but%20homeownership%20in%20the%20US%20isn't%20a%20priority%20for%20me%20in%20the%20grand%20scheme%20of%20things%20the%20way%20that%20it%20is%20for%20some%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWould%20I%20move%20to%20more%20suburban%20New%20Jersey%20so%20I%20could%20buy%20a%20house%3F%20No.%20I%20would%20not%20make%20the%20calculus%20to%20move%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20another%20city%2C%20or%20another%20state%2C%20or%20a%20suburb%20%E2%80%94%20to%20buy%20a%20house.%20That's%20my%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20first%20stepped%20foot%20in%20the%20Mallorca%20home%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20the%20first%20time%20I%20visited%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20was%20just%20smiling%20alone%20in%20this%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20so%20cool.%20I%20am%20standing%20in%20this%20beautiful%20house%20that%20I%20own.%20How%20cool%20is%20that%3F%20I%20am%20here%20on%20an%20island.%20Who%20knows%20if%20I%20ever%20would've%20found%20my%20way%20here%20otherwise%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20just%20made%20me%20so%20happy%20and%20so%20proud.%20It%20did%20make%20me%20feel%20proud%20of%20the%20accomplishment%20and%20purchasing%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20homeownership%20the%20metric%20for%20financial%20success%20that%20we%20should%20all%20be%20striving%20for%3F%20That's%20an%20open%20question%20in%20America%2C%20and%20I%20think%20everyone%20will%20view%20that%20a%20little%20bit%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeownership%20does%2C%20rightly%20or%20wrongly%2C%20feel%20like%20it%20is%20on%20that%20prescribed%20path%3A%20I%20went%20to%20high%20school%2C%20I%20went%20to%20college%2C%20I%20got%20a%20job%2C%20then%20I'm%20going%20to%20find%20a%20husband%2C%20buy%20a%20house%2C%20have%20a%20kid%2C%20have%20another%20kid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20always%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20a%20path%20that%20you%20feel%20pressure%20to%20walk%20down%20whether%20you%20want%20to%20admit%20it%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeownership%20feels%20like%20it's%20on%20that%20path%20for%20me%2C%20and%20so%20this%20was%20definitely%20a%20way%20to%20feel%20accomplished.%20It%20checked%20that%20box%20in%20a%20way%20that%20made%20sense%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-afford-buy-house-in-us-invested-europe-vacation-home-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710060122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65ea3a8b6080194819fdd4b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-afford-buy-house-in-us-invested-europe-vacation-home-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amy%20Beihl%20didn't%20want%20to%20sacrifice%20travel%20to%20own%20a%20home%2C%20so%20she%20bought%20a%20share%20of%20five%20vacation%20homes%20in%20Europe%20for%20less%20than%20an%20apartment%20in%20NYC.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcant-afford-buy-house-in-us-invested-europe-vacation-home-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20EFTA%20sign%20%24100%20bn%2015-year%20free%20trade%20agreement%3A%20Piyush%20Goyal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710060090000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F08%2Ffull%2F1709897896-8538.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-efta-sign-100-bn-15-year-free-trade-agreement-piyush-goyal-124031000149_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20European%20Free%20Trade%20Association%20(EFTA)%20members%20are%20Iceland%2C%20Liechtenstein%2C%20Norway%2C%20and%20Switzerland%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-efta-sign-100-bn-15-year-free-trade-agreement-piyush-goyal-124031000149_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22