0poetry%20collections%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EBitter%20Gourd%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3ENine%2C%3Cem%3E%20and%20a%20novel%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EC%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710057016000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10131119%2Fjr-korpa-ISlAfxGsNH4-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fif-all-poetry-is-protest-and-two-other-poems%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20no%20news%20is%20good%20news%2C%20%2F%20if%20in%20silence%20we%20must%20love%2C%20%2F%20I%20choose%20the%20bad%20over%20good%2C%20I%20choose%20not%20to%20love.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fif-all-poetry-is-protest-and-two-other-poems%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20Pitch%20To%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Voters%20While%20Launching%20Infra%20Blitz%20In%20Azamgarh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20while%20inaugurating%20projects%20worth%20Rs%2034%2C000%20Crore%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Azamgarh%2C%20said%20that%20his%20government%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20development%20across%20the%20country.%20Addressing%20a%20rally%2C%20he%20said%20that%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20there%20was%20no%20development%20in%20this%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20but%20that%20has%20now%20changed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAzamgarh%20is%20shining%20today.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20when%20an%20event%20was%20held%20in%20Delhi%20and%20people%20from%20other%20states%20used%20to%20attend%20it.%20Today%2C%20the%20event%20is%20being%20organised%20in%20Azamgarh%20and%20people%20from%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20are%20attending%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20in%20previous%20governments%20used%20to%20make%20announcements%20to%20deceive%20people...When%20I%20analyse%2C%20I%20find%20that%20announcements%20were%20made%2030-35%20years%20ago.%20They%20used%20to%20put%20up%20a%20plaque%20before%20elections%20and%20disappear%20after%20that%2C%20the%20leaders%20disappeared%20too...Today%2C%20the%20country%20can%20see%20that%20Modi%20doosri%20mitti%20ka%20insaan%20hai%20(Modi%20is%20cut%20out%20from%20a%20different%20fabric)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20event%2C%20PM%20Modi%20inaugurated%20airports%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20Shravasti%2C%20Chitrakoot%2C%20and%20Aligarh%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Maharaja%20Suhel%20Dev%20State%20University%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20constructed%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%20108%20crore.%20The%20infra%20blitz%20comes%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20dates%20for%20which%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20announced%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20though%20said%20one%20must%20not%20link%20these%20projects%20with%20elections%20and%20added%20that%20he%20sped%20up%20the%20development%20works%20to%20achieve%20the%20dream%20of%20a%20developed%20India%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20is%20scaling%20the%20heights%20of%20development%2C%20the%20venom%20of%20appeasement%20is%20weakening...So%2C%20'parivarvaadi'%20people%20are%20baffled%20and%20abusing%20Modi%20every%20day.%20They%20say%20Modi%20doesn't%20have%20a%20family%20of%20his%20own.%20They%20forget%20that%20the%20140%20crore%20people%20of%20the%20country%20is%20'Modi%20ka%20Parivar'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event%2C%20expressed%20gratitude%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20was%20the%20identity%20of%20Azamgarh%2010%20years%20back%3F%20Today%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20transformed%20Azamgarh%2C%20once%20notorious%20for%20criminal%20and%20mafia%20activities%2C%20by%20infusing%20investments%20in%20projects%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Azamgarh%20has%20not%20only%20gained%20a%20secure%20environment%20but%20has%20also%20witnessed%20the%20development%20of%20modern%20infrastructure.%20We%20extend%20our%20thanks%20to%20PM%20Modi%20for%20this%20transformative%20journey%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20inaugurated%20a%20new%20terminal%20at%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20International%20Airport%20in%20Lucknow.%20Encompassing%20a%20land%20area%20of%201%2C11%2C367%20square%20meters%2C%20the%20terminal%20includes%20a%20spacious%20basement%2C%20a%20corridor%20connecting%20T2%20and%2013%20terminals%2C%20and%20aims%20to%20accommodate%20over%2013%20million%20passengers%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20estimated%20construction%20cost%20is%20Rs%201%2C383%20crore.%20The%20new%20terminal%20features%2075%20check-in%20counters%2C%2018%20check-in%20kiosks%2C%2030%20lifts%2C%20and%20five%20escalators.%20The%20design%20and%20interiors%2C%20led%20by%20Pascal%20and%20Watson%2C%20showcase%20the%20culture%20and%20heritage%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELucknow%20International%20Airport%20Limited%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20has%20leased%20the%20airport%20for%2050%20years.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20agreement%2C%20LIAL%20pays%20a%20per-passenger%20fee%20(PPF)%20to%20the%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(AAI)%20for%20each%20domestic%20and%20international%20passenger%20using%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710057000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fkibeakbc_narendra-modi_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-pitch-to-uttar-pradesh-voters-while-launching-infra-blitz-in-azamgarh-lucknow-airport-terminal-5211238%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22P