em%20her%20anti-Hindu%20image.%20Too%20late%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20quipped%20Mr%20Malviya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BMore%20importantly%2C%20she%20needs%20to%20ensure%20no%20stones%20are%20pelted%20on%20Ram%20Navami%20processions.%20Will%20she%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20and%20the%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20Bengal%20assembly%2C%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20said%20Ms%20Banerjee%20was%20forced%20to%20take%20this%20step%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bchanging%20ground%20situation%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20fast%20changing%20ground%20situation%20in%20WB%20she%20has%20now%20realised%20that%20the%20Ram%20Bhakts%20are%20extremely%20disappointed%20with%20her.%20So%2C%20as%20a%20face%20saving%20measure%2C%20she%20felt%20%C2%A0bound%20to%20declare%20a%20holiday%20on%20Wednesday%2C%2017%20Apr%2C%202024%2C%20when%20Shree%20Ram%20Navami%20will%20be%20celebrated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20is%20yet%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20BJP%20leaders'%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20clashes%20during%20Ram%20Navami%20last%20year%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20had%20accused%20%26quot%3Boutsiders%26quot%3B%20of%20trying%20to%20disrupt%20harmony%20in%20the%20state.%20Justifying%20police%20action%20during%20the%20rally%2C%20she%20had%20questioned%20why%20people%20brought%20bulldozers%20to%20the%20religious%20procession%2C%20carried%20arms%20and%20danced%20with%20a%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20already%20in%20attack%20mode%20over%20the%20Sandeshkhali%20row%2C%20in%20which%20a%20strongman%20and%20former%20Trinamool%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%20was%20arrested%20last%20week.%20Shahjahan%20faces%20multiple%20charges%20of%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land-grabbing%20in%20the%20island%20village%20in%20North%2024%20Paraganas%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuvendu%20Adhikari%20will%20address%20a%20meeting%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20today%20while%20the%20Trinamool%20prepares%20for%20a%20massive%20rally%20at%20the%20iconic%20Brigade%20Parade%20Grounds%20in%20Kolkata.%20Sources%20say%20Ms%20Banerjee%20could%20also%20declare%20the%20Trinamool%20candidates%20at%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710056460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fcv5hfqkg_mamata-banerjee_625x300_18_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-declares-public-holiday-on-ram-navami-bjps-blue-with-rage-jibe-5210830%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ram%20Navami%20on%20April%2018%20this%20year%20has%20been%20declared%20a%20public%20holiday%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20move%20came%20%26quot%3Btoo%20late%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20BJP%2C%20claiming%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20wants%20to%20redeem%20her%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%20image%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-declares-public-holiday-on-ram-navami-bjps-blue-with-rage-jibe-5210830%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-declares-public-holiday-on-ram-navami-bjps-blue-with-rage-jibe-5210830%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbengal-declares-public-holiday-on-ram-navami-bjps-blue-with-rage-jibe-5210830%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Jaya%20cried%20after%20watching%20Rekha-Big%20B's%20scenes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710056326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108365159%2Cimgsize-54604.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-jaya-bachchan-cried-after-watching-rekha-and-amitabh-bachchans-intimae-scenes%2Farticleshow%2F108365171.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat