%20Law%20%26amp%3B%20Justice%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20leaves%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20limping%20with%20only%20one%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20namely%2C%20Shri%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20to%20oversee%20the%20ensuing%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20transpired%20thus%20far%20is%20too%20serious%20a%20matter%20that%20casts%20a%20shadow%20on%20the%20entire%20electoral%20process%20on%20which%20some%20of%20us%20and%20many%20political%20parties%20have%20expressed%20our%20concerns%20time%20and%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20view%2C%20the%20abrupt%20and%20somewhat%20inexplicable%20exit%20of%20Shri%20Goel%20raises%20the%20following%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20his%20dissent%20on%20the%20way%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20been%20trying%20to%20interfere%20with%20the%20electoral%20process%20in%20several%20ways%20vitiating%20its%20sanctity%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20doubts%20about%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20use%20of%20EVMs%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20he%20express%20his%20concern%20at%20the%20way%20the%20political%20executive%20has%20pressured%20the%20SBI%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20details%20of%20the%20EBS%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWas%20there%20any%20proposal%20from%20Shri%20Goel%20to%20freeze%20the%20residual%20amounts%20received%20by%20the%20political%20parties%20under%20the%20EBS%20to%20prevent%20their%20use%20in%20the%20ensuing%20elections%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20propose%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20nominees%20from%20the%20Boards%20of%20BEL%2C%20ECIL%20and%20SBI%20be%20withdrawn%20to%20maintain%20the%20sanctity%20the%20electoral%20process%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20Shri%20Goel%20express%20his%20dissent%20on%20any%20other%20matter%20that%20would%20have%20displeased%20the%20political%20executive%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20the%20highest%20within%20the%20political%20executive%20force%20Shri%20Goel%20to%20tender%20his%20resignation%20to%20clear%20the%20way%20for%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20machinations%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20earnestly%20believe%20that%20the%20nation%20expects%20an%20independent%20inquiry%20into%20the%20above%20questions%20as%20they%20concern%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20democratic%20processes%20in%20India%20and%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy%20itself.%20Such%20an%20inquiry%20needs%20to%20be%20independent%20of%20the%20political%20executive%20and%20preferably%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20entrusted%20by%20your%20office%20to%20a%20panel%20of%20the%20sitting%20members%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPending%20such%20an%20enquiry%2C%20your%20office%2C%20invoking%20the%20authority%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20order%20that%20(i)%20no%20announcement%20of%20the%20election%20schedule%20be%20made%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20(ii)%20no%20policy%20decisions%2F%20announcements%20be%20made%20by%20the%20political%20executive%2C%20and%20(iii)%20no%20expenditure%20should%20be%20incurred%20by%20any%20political%20party%20from%20the%20funds%20received%20under%20the%20EBS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespected%20Rashtrapati%20Ji%2C%20your%20intervention%20at%20this%20critical%20juncture%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20nation%20is%20necessary%20and%20perhaps%20unavoidable%20to%20preserve%20the%20democratic%20character%20of%20our%20Constitution%20and%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20I%2C%20as%20a%20senior%20citizen%2C%20deeply%20concerned%20with%20the%20future%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20appeal%20to%20you%20to%20step%20in%2C%20act%20decisively%20and%20ensure%20that%20the%20dreams%20of%20Dr%20B%20R%20Ambedkar%20and%20the%20other%20framers%20of%20our%20Constitution%20are%20fulfilled%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERespectfully%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EE%20A%20S%20Sarma%3Cbr%3E%5Cn10th%20March%202024%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710055194000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2