0the%20'Test%20Cricket%20Incentive%20Scheme'%20will%20serve%20as%20an%20additional%20reward%20structure%20on%20top%20of%20the%20existing%20match%20fee%20for%20Test%20matches%2C%20set%20at%20INR%2015%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20thrilled%20to%20introduce%20the%20'Test%20Cricket%20Incentive%20Scheme%2C'%20reaffirming%20our%20dedication%20to%20the%20well-being%20and%20encouragement%20of%20our%20senior%20men%20cricketers.%20This%20initiative%20aligns%20with%20our%20vision%20of%20promoting%20Test%20cricket%20as%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20the%20sport%2C%26quot%3B%20BCCI%20president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBCCI%20secretary%20Jay%20Shah%20stated%20that%20the%20incentive%20would%20serve%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Badditional%20reward%20structure%26quot%3B%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20match%20fees%20of%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20for%20players.%20The%20move%20will%20provide%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20growth%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bstability%26quot%3B%20to%20players%20who%20participate%20keenly%20in%20the%20most%20revered%20format%20of%20the%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20'Test%20Cricket%20Incentive%20Scheme'%20is%20a%20progressive%20move%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20significance%20of%20Test%20cricket.%20This%20pioneering%20initiative%20is%20intricately%20aligned%20with%20our%20broader%20vision%2C%20which%20is%20focussed%20around%20the%20promotion%20of%20Test%20cricket%20as%20the%20undisputed%20pinnacle%20of%20the%20sport.%20As%20we%20embark%20on%20this%20journey%2C%20we%20are%20not%20only%20recognizing%20the%20invaluable%20contributions%20of%20our%20players%20but%20also%20fostering%20an%20environment%20that%20values%20and%20prioritizes%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20traditional%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20This%20scheme%20is%20designed%20to%20inspire%20our%20cricketers%20to%20contribute%20their%20absolute%20best%20to%20the%20longer%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20It%20is%20a%20recognition%20of%20the%20unique%20challenges%20and%20demands%20that%20Test%20cricket