ip%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchoice%20of%20history%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20significance%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20ties%20has%20become%20more%20%E2%80%9Cprominent%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20light%20of%20current%20changes%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZardari%2C%20the%20husband%20of%20late%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Benazir%20Bhutto%20was%20overwhelmingly%20elected%20as%20the%2014th%20President%20of%20Pakistan%20on%20Saturday%2C%20becoming%20the%20only%20civilian%20president%20of%20the%20coup-prone%20country%20for%20a%20second%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZardari%2C%20the%20co-chairperson%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%2C%20was%20the%20joint%20candidate%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20of%20the%20PPP%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20message%20to%20Zardari%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Xi%20said%20%26quot%3BChina%20and%20Pakistan%20are%20good%20neighbours%2C%20good%20friends%2C%20good%20partners%20and%20good%20brothers%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20two%20countries'%20iron-clad%20friendship%20is%20a%20choice%20of%20history%20and%20a%20precious%20treasure%20of%20the%20two%20peoples.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20two%20countries%20have%20in%20recent%20years%20maintained%20close%20high-level%20exchanges%2C%20supported%20each%20other%20on%20issues%20concerning%20their%20respective%20core%20interests%20and%20major%20concerns%2C%20achieved%20fruitful%20results%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20and%20maintained%20a%20high%20level%20of%20development%20of%20bilateral%20relations%2C%26quot%3B%20state-run%20Xinhua%20news%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20objected%20to%20China%20over%20the%20USD%2060%20billion%20CPEC%20connecting%20China's%20Xinjiang%20with%20Gwadar%20port%20in%20Balochistan%20as%20it%20is%20being%20laid%20through%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%