rticles%2F15%2F5301%2F2023%2Fessd-15-5301-2023.html)%3B%20Global%20Carbon%20Project%202023%20(https%3A%2F%2Fwww.globalcarbonproject.org%2Fcarbonbudget%2F)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20of%20course%2C%20is%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20already%20built%20a%20world%20that%E2%80%99s%20now%20well%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fthe-human-animal-in-the-circle-of-life%5C%22%3Estate%20of%20ecological%20overshoot%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20we%E2%80%99re%20locked%20into%20capitalism%E2%80%99s%20requirement%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fof-mice-and-men-energy-and-cancer%5C%22%3Egrowth%20in%20consumption%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20to%20keep%20the%20present%20system%20afloat%3A%20to%20keep%20the%20goods%20flowing%2C%20the%20steel%20and%20concrete%20rising%2C%20the%20institutions%20flush%20with%20resources%20for%20research%20and%20education%20and%20policymaking%2C%20the%20factories%20supplied%20with%20raw%20materials%20and%20industrial%20chemicals%E2%80%94many%20of%20which%20are%20directly%20sourced%20from%20petroleum.%20As%20a%20living%20system%20set%20upon%20a%20trajectory%20of%20unabated%20growth%2C%20our%20economy%20requires%20the%20massive%20overconsumption%20of%20both%20energy%20and%20materials%2C%20even%20as%20it%20destroys%20the%20living%20systems%20of%20the%20world%20upon%20which%20it%20depends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20crux%20of%20our%20predicament%3A%20Consumption%2C%20growth%2C%20socioeconomic%20wellbeing%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20inequalities%2C%20exploitation%2C%20pollution%2C%20species%20genocide%2C%20ecosystem%20annihilation%2C%20and%20the%20burning%20of%20fossil%20fuels%20form%20a%20nexus%20of%20interdependencies%20that%20feed%20and%20perpetuate%20one%20another%20as%20the%20basis%20of%20modern%20global%20civilisation.%20This%20system%20is%20both%20unsustainable%20over%20time%20as%20well%20as%20immediately%20destructive%20for%20great%20multitudes%2C%20both%20human%20and%20non-human%2C%20even%20while%20we%20have%20made%20it%20foundational%20to%20the%20dreams%20and%20livelihoods%20of%20billions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ctable%3E%5Cn%3Ctbody%3E%5Cn%3Ctr%3E%5Cn%3Ctd%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Green%20Revolution%20deployed%20thirsty%2C%20high-yielding%20strains%20of%20wheat%20and%20rice%20that%20grew%20well%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20artificial%20fertilisers%2C%20herbicides%2C%20and%20pesticides.%20As%20with%20any%20%E2%80%98progress%20trap%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20short-term%20benefits%20gained%20cannot%20overcome%20the%20long-term%20costs%20incurred%2C%20including%20soil%20destruction%3B%20groundwater%20depletion%3B%20chemical%20pollution%20of%20land%2C%20water%2C%20and%20people%3B%20loss%20of%20insects%20and%20other%20biodiversity%3B%20narrowing%20of%20the%20Indian%20diet%3B%20and%20extinction%20of%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fgrains-of-life-how-chotanagpurs-adivasis-are-reviving-native-varieties-of-rice%5C%22%3Eone%20lakh%20varieties%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%2C%20shrinking%20the%20available%20gene%20pool%20for%20food%20grains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftd%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftbody%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ftable%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20combustible%20fossil%20revolution%E2%80%94with%20a%20special%20emphasis%20on%20oil%E2%80%94absolutely%20underwrites%20the%20modern%20way%20of%20life.%20It%20has%20provided%20continuous%20growth%20in%20energy%20use%2C%20which%20%3Cem%3Ecannot%3C%2Fem%3E%20be%20replicated%20by%20less%20concentrated%2C%20more%20unreliable%2C%20and%20seasonally%20or%20diurnally%20limited%20renewable%20sources.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20already%20know%20this.%20Why%20else%20would%20we%20Indians%20have%20argued%20for%20entitlements%20to%20burn%20more%20fossils%2C%20justified%20only%20by%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20economic%20dominance%20by%20having%20done%20it%20first%3F%20If%20we%20believed%20%E2%80%98renewables%E2%80%99%20were%20a%20complete%20answer%2C%20we%20would%20gladly%20leapfrog%20the%20need%20for%20combustible%20fossils%20and%20build%20the%20great%20and%20%E2%80%98clean%E2%80%99%20Indian%20industrial%20economy.%20But%20despite%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98hope%E2%80%99%20elites%20declaim%20around%20%E2%80%98greening%E2%80%99%20our%20energy%20systems%2C%20we%20intuitively%20understand%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20way%20to%20have%20the%20%E2%80%98developed%2C%E2%80%99%20capitalist-consumerist%20economy%20without%20breaking%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20all%20the%20%E2%80%98renewable%E2%80%99%20energy%E2%80%94which%20is%20delivered%20to%20us%20only%20through%20installations%20that%20are%20%3Cem%3Enot%20at%20all%20renewable%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20%3Cem%3Emust%20be%20built%20and%20re-built%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20every%20few%20decades%E2%80%94thus%20far%20deployed%20haven%E2%80%99t%20begun%20to%20reduce%20our%20fossil%20fuel%20consumption.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fourworldindata.org%2Fgrapher%2Felectricity-prod-source-stacked%5C%22%3Eonly%20added%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20our%20overall%20energy%20consumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20581px)%2085vw%2C%20581px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22581%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution-300x212.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F10112945%2Fglobal-energy-substitution-1024x723.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-700960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22410%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERenewable%20energy%20sources%20haven%E2%80%99t%20reduced%20our%20demand%20for%20combustible%20fossils.%20They%20have%20only%20