%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20use%20of%20tanks%20in%20World%20War%201%20or%20the%20development%20of%20supersonic%20fighter%20jets%20after%20World%20War%202%2C%20'disruptive%20technology'%20has%20changed%20the%20status%20quo%20between%20factions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20summit%2C%20General%20Pande%20focused%20on%20access%20to%20such%20technology%20by%20non-state%20actors%2C%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20security%20of%20the%20country%20and%20said%20information%2C%20cyber%2C%20and%20space%20warfare%20have%20been%20added%20to%20the%20domain%20of%20conflicts.%20The%20Army%20chief%20said%20the%20adversary%2C%20with%20access%20to%20such%20technology%2C%20can%20initiate%20a%20low-threshold%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Deputy%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20of%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwarontherocks.com%2F2014%2F08%2Fpeace-and-war-the-space-between%2F%5C%22%3ENadia%20Schadlow%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20space%20between%20war%20and%20peace%20is%20not%20an%20empty%20one%20-%20but%20a%20landscape%20churning%20with%20political%2C%20economic%2C%20and%20security%20competitions%20that%20require%20constant%20attention.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Disruptive%20Technology'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20democratization%20of%20technology%20led%20to%20the%20easy%20acquisition%20of%20AI%2C%20which%20can%20be%20used%20to%20direct%20targeted%20attacks.%20The%20use%20of%20semi-autonomous%20and%20autonomous%20drones%2C%20which%20are%20powered%20by%20AI%2C%20in%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20the%20attacks%20in%20the%20Red%20Sea%20have%20forced%20states%20to%20change%20their%20strategy.%20The%20US-led%20alliance%20in%20the%20Gulf%20is%20tracking%20the%20attacks%20but%20is%20yet%20to%20nip%20it%20in%20the%20bud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrones%20can%20carry%20out%20missions%20at%20low%20cost%20and%20have%20blunted%20the%20asymmetry.%20The%20US%20and%20UK%20are%20arming%20Ukraine%20with%20AI-powered%20drones%20to%20carry%20out%20precision%20strikes.%20Ukraine's%20domestic%20production%20of%20drones%20has%20risen%20significantly%20since%20the%20war%20began%20in%202022%20and%20the%20need%20has%20created%20a%20giant%20war%20lab%20and%20the%20country%20is%20producing%20more%20drones%20than%20it%20could%20purchase.%20The%20UK%20has%20increased%20the%20funding%20by%20125%20million%20pounds%20and%20will%20supply%20over%2010%2C000%20drones%20to%20Ukraine.%20Houthi%20rebels%2C%20backed%20by%20Yemen%2C%20have%20used%20autonomous%20platforms%20to%20target%20ships%20in%20the%20Gulf.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F3un9tu5g_ukraine-drone_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20use%20of%20drones%20indicates%20a%20doctrinal%20shift%20and%20robots%20are%20here%20to%20play%20an%20important%20role.%2010-15%25%20of%20robots%20will%20be%20there%20in%20future%20forces%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fis-india-ready-to-face-emerging-threats-what-experts-say-5195098%5C%22%3ESameer%20Joshi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20defence%20expert%20said%20at%20the%20summit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOff-the-shelf%20disruptive%20technologies%20have%20helped%20conventionally%20weaker%20states%20use%20methods%20to%20fight%20a%20cost-efficient%2C%20sustainable%20fight%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20battlefield%20longer.%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20air%20defence%20system%20uses%20AI%20to%20intercept%20incoming%20rockets.%20The%202021%20Israeli%20offensive%20against%20Palestinians%20is%20called%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-war-over-14-000-dead-in-gaza-how-israel-is-using-ai-to-conduct-air-strikes-4624859%5C%22%3E%20first%20'AI%20war'%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Israel%20used%20AI%20tools%20like%20'Gospel'%2C%20'Alchemist'%2C%20and%20'Depth%20of%20Wisodm'%20to%20conduct%20precision%20strikes%20on%20targets%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECyberattacks%20on%20state%20infrastructure%20through%20Malware%20have%20posed%20challenges%20for%20several%20years.%20The%20malware%20attack%20on%20the%20servers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faiims-delhi-server-attack-was-by-chinese-5-physical-servers-infiltrated-by-hackers-data-retrieved-now-government-sources-3605639%5C%22%3EAIIMS%20Delhi%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20one%20such%20example.%20The%20attack%20was%20by%20the%20Chinese%2C%20FIR%20details%20that%20the%20attack%20had%20originated%20from%20China.%20Of%20100%20servers%20(40%20physical%20and%2060%20virtual)%2C%20five%20physical%20servers%20were%20successfully%20infiltrated%20by%20the%20hackers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20healthcare%20providers%20in%20the%20US%20have%20struggled%20to%20make%20payments%20following%20a%20ransomware%20attack%2C%20which%20reportedly%20originated%20from%20Russia.%20The%20Colonial%20Pipeline%20attack%20on%20US%20oil%20infrastructure%20was%20the%20biggest%20in%20history.%20Reports%20claimed%20that%20a%20Russian%20group%20named%20DarkSide%20was%20responsible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20elements%20in%20India's%20new%20criminal%20laws%20is%20the%20inclusion%20of%20%26quot%3Bthreat%20to%20economic%20security%26quot%3B%20under%20the%20definition%20of%20an%20%26quot%3Bact%20of%20terror%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConcerns%20over%20Deep%20Fakes%20have%20been%20raised%20even%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Its%20use%20in%20information%20warfare%20in%20generating%20fake%20news%2C%20especially%20during%20a%20crisis.%20Information%20warfare%20is%20as%20essential%20as%20firepower%20in%20a%20battle%20to%20psychologically%20dominate%20the%20warring%20faction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%20last%20year%2C%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20outlining%20security%20measures%20for%20AI.%20The%20Deputy%20White%20House%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20Bruce%20Reed%20said%20Biden's%20interest%20in%20AI%20was%20partly%20fuelled%20after%20watching%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2024%2Ffeb%2F23%2Fai-deepfakes-come-of-age-as-billions-prepare-to-vote-in-a-bumper-year-of-elections%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Mission%3A%20Impossible%20-%20Dead%20Reckoning%20Part%20One.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20chief%20at%20the%20summit%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20happening%20amidst%20legacy%20challenges%20of%20unsettled%20borders%20continue%2C%26quot%3B%20-%20An%20indirect%20reference%20to%20issues%20with%20China%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'China's%20Three%20Warfare%20Strategy'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202003%2C%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party's%20Central%20Committee%20and%20the%20Central%20Military%20Commission%20approved%20the%20'Three%20Warfare%20Strategy'%20to%20guide%20the%20People's%20Liberation%20Army's%20political%20and%20information%20warfighting.%20The%20three%20elements%20of%20the%20strategy%20are%20Public%20Opinion%2C%20Information%20and%20Legal%20Warfare.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-09%2Fd41je53g_india-china-border-arunachal-pradesh-reuters_625x300_02_September_20.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20the%20border%20conflict%20in%20Ladakh%20as%20a%20reference%2C%20China%20used%20legacy%20claims%20like%20the%201962%20reference%20line%2C%20and%201959%20claims%20in%20Ladakh%20to%20justify%20its%20aggressive%20military%20posture.%20The%20dissemination%20of%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20related%20to%20the%20Galwan%20clash%20and%20st