ised%20them.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-jamie-dimon-jp-morgan-chase-richest-men-in-banking-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChase%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20billionaire%20hedge-fund%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fray-dalio-warning-capitalism-american-dream-inequality-economics-billionaire-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERay%20Dalio%3C%2Fa%3E%20appear%20to%20be%20hedging%20on%20their%20doom-and-gloom%20predictions%20for%20the%20US%20economy%20after%20warning%20for%20some%20time%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnext-recession-economy-outlook-unemployment-rate-rise-february-jobs-report-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecession%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20imminent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%202022%2C%20Dalio%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketwatch.com%2Fstory%2Fray-dalio-says-stocks-bonds-have-further-to-fall-sees-u-s-recession-arriving-in-2023-or-2024-11663777067%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarketWatch%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%2C%20as%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20suffer%2C%20the%20US%20will%20likely%20slide%20into%20a%20recession%20in%202023%20or%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Dimon%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2022%2F10%2F10%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-warns-us-likely-to-tip-into-recession-soon.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20the%20US%20economy%20was%20%26quot%3Bactually%20still%20doing%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20believed%20that%20runaway%20inflation%2C%20high%20interest%20rates%2C%20and%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20could%20cause%20the%20US%20to%20go%20into%20a%20recession%20in%20%26quot%3Bsix%20to%20nine%20months.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20high-profile%20investors%2C%20billionaires%2C%20and%20economists%20anticipated%20a%20painful%20economic%20storm%20in%20