New%20Yorker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20just%20very%20energy%20intensive%2C%26quot%3B%20de%20Vries%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-industry-energy-study-small-country-enviroment-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20of%20these%20AI%20servers%20can%20already%20consume%20as%20much%20power%20as%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20UK%20households%20combined.%20So%20the%20numbers%20add%20up%20really%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20estimating%20how%20much%20electricity%20the%20booming%20AI%20industry%20consumes%20is%20tough%20to%20pin%20down.%20There's%20considerable%20variability%20in%20how%20large%20AI%20models%20operate%2C%20and%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20which%20have%20been%20driving%20the%20boom%20%E2%80%94%20haven't%20been%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eexactly%20forthcoming%20about%20their%20energy%20use%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24066646%2Fai-electricity-energy-watts-generative-consumption%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20paper%2C%20however%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ede%20Vries%20came%20up%20with%20a%20rough%20calculation%20based%20on%20numbers%20put%20out%20by%20Nvidia%20%E2%80%94%20which%20some%20have%20dubbed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-cathie-wood-ark-cisco-ai-internet-bubble-microchips-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bthe%20Cisco%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20figures%20from%20New%20Street%20Research%20reported%20by%20CNBC%2C%20the%20chipmaker%20has%20about%2095%25%20of%20the%20market%20share%20for%20graphics%20processors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Vries%20estimated%20in%20the%20paper%20that%20by%202027%2C%20the%20entire%20AI%20sector%20will%20consume%20between%2085%20to%20134%20terawatt-hours%20(a%20billion%20times%20a%20kil