rican%20Samoa%20has%20turned%20out%20unexpected%20primary%20results%20before.%20In%202020%2C%20billionaire%20Michael%20Bloomberg's%20only%20win%20in%20the%20Democratic%20primaries%20came%20from%20the%20territory.%20Despite%20the%20odds%2C%20Palmer%20hopes%20his%20win%20there%20will%20create%20momentum%20for%20his%20campaign%20in%20states%20like%20Arizona%2C%20Kansas%2C%20and%20Missouri.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20able%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20position%20and%20get%20it%20sometimes%20better%20than%20even%20if%20you%20ask%20me%20the%20question.%20If%20you%20ask%20me%2C%20I'm%20too%20verbose%20and%20I%20take%2060%20seconds%2C%20but%20it%20gives%20you%20a%20really%20tight%20answer%20that's%20like%2010%20seconds%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Palmer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20most%20people%20are%20blown%20away%20by%20our%20campaign%20using%20this%20technology%20because%20it%20would%20have%20taken%20like%20%2410%20million%20to%20build%20five%20years%20ago.%20And%20that's%20partly%20because%20AI%20has%20gotten%20so%20much%20better.%20But%20it's%20also%20because%20I'm%20the%20first%20technology%20entrepreneur%20who's%20ever%20run%20for%20president%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%2080%20years%20old%2C%20I'm%20actually%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20my%20entrepreneurial%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20campaign%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20regarding%20whether%20the%20incumbent%20president%20plans%20to%20use%20AI%20in%20his%20reelection%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Biden's%20voice%20was%20spoofed%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-behind-biden-robocall-said-did-it-to-make-difference-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20robocall%3C%2Fa%3E%20discouraging%20constituents%20from%20voting%20in%20the%20New%20Hampshire%20primary%2C%20resulting%20in%20Biden%20calling%20for%20a%20ban%20on%20using%20the%20tech%20for%20voice%20im