dgets-news%2Fapple-watch-series-9-is-now-cheaper-than-watch-series-8-no-conditions-apply%2Farticleshow%2F108355031.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22TDP%20Returns%20to%20NDA%20Fold%20As%20it%20Seals%20Alliance%20with%20BJP%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Assembly%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09211120%2FFotoJet-7-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20on%20Saturday%20(March%209)%20announced%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%20and%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20Party%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20assembly%20elections%2C%20which%20will%20be%20held%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20the%20three%20parties%20said%20that%20their%20coming%20together%20with%20the%20two%20parties%20will%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20in%20reaching%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20and%20TDP%20have%20a%20very%20old%20relationship%20together.%20TDP%20joined%20NDA%20in%201996%20and%20has%20worked%20together%20successfully%20in%20Atal%20Ji%E2%80%99s%20and%20Narendra%20Modi%C2%A0%20Ji%E2%80%99%20government.%20In%C2%A0%202014%2C%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%C2%A0%20fought%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20and%20assembly%20election%20together.%20The%C2%A0%20JSP%C2%A0%20had%20supported%20the%202014%C2%A0%20general%20and%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20alliance%20has%20been%20sealed%2C%20seat-sharing%20arrangements%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20formally%20announced.%20The%20BJP%20said%20that%20the%20modalities%20will%20be%20deliberated%20in%20a%20day%20or%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20reporters%20after%20the%20alliance%20was%20sealed%2C%20Naidu%20said%20that%20it%20will%20be%20a%20sweep%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAndhra%20Pradesh%20has%20been%20destroyed%20badly.%20The%20BJP%20and%20the%20TDP%20coming%20together%20is%20a%20win-win%20situation%20for%20the%20country%20and%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20second%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20BJP%20chief%20J.P.%20Nadda%2C%20Naidu%20and%20Jana%20Sena%20chief%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TDP%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fandhras-telugu-desam-party-pulls-out-of-modi-government%5C%22%3Epulled%20out%20of%20the%20NDA%3C%2Fa%3E%20(National%20Democratic%20Alliance)%20in%202018%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20grant%20special%20category%20status%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20TDP%20launched%20a%20%E2%80%98dharma%20poratam%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98fight%20for%20justice%E2%80%99%20and%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Ftdp-quits-nda-chandrababu-naidu-s-party-moves-no-confidence-motion-cong-and-left-to-support-move%2Fstory-zEOA5kDvoNU5GHs0yAfI1H.html%5C%22%3Emoved%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20NDA%20government.%20Labelling%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20a%20%E2%80%98terrorist%E2%80%99%2C%20Naidu%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fchandrababu-naidu-drags-pm-modis-wife-name-for-comments-on-son-lokesh%2Farticleshow%2F67929131.cms%5C%22%3Eaccused%3C%2Fa%3E%20him%20of%20%E2%80%9Cestranging%E2%80%9D%20his%20wife.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202019%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20declared%20that%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20NDA%20were%20permanently%20closed%20for%20Naidu%2C%20who%20he%20labelled%20as%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5