ve-cyprus-for-gaza-13090655%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20National%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20Decision%20to%20Contest%203%20Lok%20Sabha%20Seats%20Exposes%20Fissures%20Within%20INDIA%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11163902%2Fomar-mehbooba.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20National%20Conference%E2%80%99s%20(NC)%20decision%20to%20contest%20from%20three%20out%20of%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20irked%20the%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20(PDP)%2C%20its%20Gupkar%20alliance%20constituent%2C%20raising%20clouds%20of%20uncertainty%20over%20the%20fate%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cunified%20fight%E2%80%9D%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20six%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20Ladakh%2C%20the%20PDP%2C%20which%20has%20suffered%20a%20series%20of%20desertions%20in%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20is%20reportedly%20eager%20to%20contest%20the%20upcoming%20election%20from%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20seat%2C%20the%20home%20turf%20of%20party%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20that%20his%20party%20would%20contest%20all%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20exposed%20the%20fissures%20within%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20with%20the%20PDP%20chief%20also%20suggesting%20that%20her%20party%20might%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20Friday%20(March%209)%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20his%20party%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20heads%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20much%20scope%E2%80%9D%20for%20negotiations%20(with%20the%20PDP)%20on%20seat%20sharing%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20out%20the%20PDP.%20The%20situation%20has%20kept%20the%20party%20out%20of%20this%20election%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20told%20the%20(INDIA)%20alliance%20that%20our%20doors%20are%20open%20(for%20seat%20sharing%20with%20the%20PDP)%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20but%20that%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20they%20behave%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20query%20that%20the%20PDP%20was%20eager%20to%20put%20up%20its%20candidate%20on%20the%20Anantnag-Rajouri%20parliamentary%20seat%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20it%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cillogical%E2%80%9D%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhich%20(brand%20of)%20politics%20says%20that%20the%20parties%20which%20stood%20at%20number%20one%20and%20number%20two%20in%20the%20last%20parliamentary%20election%20should%20cede%20the%20contest%20to%20a%20party%20which%20was%20at%20number%20three%2C%20and%20that%20too%20on%20a%20seat%20where%20their%20influence%20is%20nowhere%20to%20be%20seen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENC%E2%80%99s%20Hasnain%20Masoodi%20is%20the%20sitting%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20from%20the%20Anantnag%20parliamentary%20seat%20that%20was%20rearranged%20to%20include%20Rajouri%20and%20most%20areas%20of%20the%20Poonch%20district%20across%20Pir%20Panjal%20in%20Jammu%2C%20following%20the%202022%20delimitation%20exercise%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20won%20the%20Anantnag%20seat%20(in%20the%202019%20polls)%20and%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20the%20second%20spot%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abdullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20coercing%20anyone.%20If%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20or%20Priyanka%20Gandhi-Vadra%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20contest%20from%20there%2C%20we%20will%20happily%20vacate%20it%20without%20hesitation.%20But%20since%20we%20have%20won%20the%20seat%2C%20we%20will%20not%20leave%20it%20for%20any%20other%20party.%20It%20is%20our%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20displeasure%20at%20the%20tweets%20of%20Mehbooba%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20Iltija%20Mufti%2C%20without%20naming%20her%2C%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20the%20PDP%20leaders%2C%20despite%20being%20part%20of%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%2C%20have%20targeted%20the%20NC%20more%20than%20they%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20during%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20annual%20Raising%20Day%20function%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20target%20the%20National%20Conference%20in%20their%20speeches%20and%20tweets%20and%20social%20media.%20We%20are%20now%20being%20dragged%20into%20the%20elections%20in%20Pakistan%20also.%20What%20kind%20of%20a%20coalition%20dharma%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20joined%20hands%20with%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20to%20target%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20(NC%20president)%20and%20our%20party%20through%20Twitter%2C%20using%20the%20platform%20of%20the%20PDP.%20Maintaining%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20coalition%20is%20not%20only%20our%20responsibility.%20Unless%20those%20who%20have%20a%20habit%20of%20targeting%20NC%20mend%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20any%20big%20hopes%20from%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20NC%20vice-president%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdullah%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20recent%20tweets%20by%20Iltija%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Mehbooba%E2%80%99s%20media%20advisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20tweets%2C%20the%20PDP%20chief%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20without%20taking%20names%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20rigging%20in%20Pakistan%20elections%2C%20which%20has%20kept%20Imran%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20party%20out%20of%20the%20government%2C%20had%20%E2%80%9Cuncanny%20similarities%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmass%20electoral%20fraud%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%201987%20assembly%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20historians%20and%20writers%20maintain%20that%20the%20NC%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20rigging%20of%20the%201987%20elections%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20which%20is%20widely%20believed%20to%20have%20become%20a%20starting%20point%20for%20the%20full-blown%20armed%20insurgency%20that%20is%20in%20its%2035th%20year%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20tweet%2C%20Iltija%20posted%20a%20sarcastic%20emoji%20to%20mock%20the%20NC%20after%20former%20Union%20minister%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20claimed%20that%20the%20party%20was%20seeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20PMO%20only%20in%20night%20hours.%20Both%20these%20tweets%20were%20posted%20by%20Sarah%20Hayat%20Shah%2C%20an%20NC%20spokesperson%2C%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%20after%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20media%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Omar%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cunfortunate%E2%80%9D%20remarks%2C%20Mufti%20told%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20that%20she%20had%20earlier%20conveyed%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20leadership%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20the%20NC%20president%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Ctallest%20leader%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20who%20should%20take%20the%20final%20call%20on%20the%20seat-sharing%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20big%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20today%20and%20the%20announcement%20%5Bby%20Abdullah%5D%20is%20a%20serious%20setback%20to%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20cause%20and%20unity.%20What%20the%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%2C%20a%20PAGD%20%5BPeople%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20for%20Gupkar%20Declaration%5D%20member%20has%20unfortunately%20achieved%20it.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20changed%20goalposts.%20Where%20we%20could%20come%20together%20to%20fight%20the%20bigger%20enemy%2C%20today%20we%20are%20face%20to%20face%20with%20each%20other%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20raising%20questions%20about%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20her%20party%20would%20pull%20out%20of%20the%20upcoming%20election%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccause%20of%20unity%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20PDP%20chief%20accused%20the%20Union%20government%20of%20making%20attempts%20to%20break%20the%20Gupkar%20alliance%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20it%20is%20the%20face%20of%20resistance%20against%20the%20BJP%E2%80%9D%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20PDP%20may%20be%20down%20but%20we%20are%20not%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mufti%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20take%20our%20case%20to%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20and%20let%20them%20decide.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20take%20the%20voice%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20to%20the%20parliament%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20voices%20from%20J%26amp%3BK%20will%20be%20watched%20in%20the%20parliament%20by%20not%20just%20the%20people%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20but%20more%20than%2020%20crore%20Muslims%20whose%20houses%20and%20mosques%20are%20being%20demolished%2C%20and%20over%2080%20crore%20Hindus%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20PDP%20would%20make%20the%20announcement%20on%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20after%20consultations%20with%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709986052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F11163902%2Fomar-mehbooba.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjk-national-conferences-decision-to-contest-3-lok-sabha-seats-exposes-fissures-within-india-bloc%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20chief%20also%20suggested%20that%20her%20party%20might%20go%20solo%20in%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20NC's%20Omar%20Abdullah%20said%20that%20his%20party%20has%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20heads%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20that%20there%20was%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20much%20scope%E2%80%9D%20for%20negotiations%20(with%20the%20PDP)%20on%20seat%20sharing%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjk-national-conferences-decision-to-contest-3-lok-sabha-seats-exposes-fissures-within-india-bloc%22%2C%22cdnAmp