s%20have%20warned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A82%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffrog-species-threatened-by-france-and-europes-taste-for-frogs-legs-experts-warn-macron-13090629%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Modi%20in%20Kaziranga%3A%20Congress%20Poses%20Four%20Questions%20on%20Security%20Situation%20in%20Northeast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09151958%2FGINULmyWEAAyNn9.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20embarked%20on%20an%20elephant%20and%20jeep%20safari%20in%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Kaziranga%20National%20Park%20and%20Tiger%20Reserve%20in%20Assam%20on%20Saturday%2C%20March%209%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20party%E2%80%99s%20communications%20charge%2C%20Jairam%20Ramesh%2C%20posted%20four%20questions%20addressing%20Modi%20on%20X%20(formerly%2C%20Twitter)%20regarding%20the%20security%20situation%20in%20the%20Northeast%20region.%20Here%20are%20the%20questions%20and%20accompanying%20text%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%E2%80%99re%20glad%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20found%20time%20amidst%20his%20various%20travels%20to%20spend%20today%20morning%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20an%20iconic%20national%20park%20which%20owes%20much%20to%20the%20great%20interest%20shown%20both%20by%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20However%20beyond%20Kaziranga%2C%20here%20are%20four%20questions%20for%20him%20on%20the%20increasingly%20disturbed%20situation%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20Northeast%20of%20India%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E1.%20On%20June%2019th%2C%202020%2C%20at%20the%20all-party%20meet%20on%20China%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20declared%20that%20not%20a%20single%20Chinese%20soldier%20had%20crossed%20over%20into%20Indian%20territory.%20By%20giving%20a%20public%20clean%20chit%20to%20China%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20tied%20his%20own%20hands%2C%20and%20failed%20to%20take%20action%20to%20restore%20the%20status%20quo%20after%20Chinese%20aggression.%20Chinese%20troops%20continue%20to%20deny%20Indian%20citizens%20access%20to%20grazing%20lands%20and%20Indian%20patrols%20access%20to%20strategic%20spots%20along%20the%20LAC%20%E2%80%93%20where%20they%20previously%20had%20unimpeded%20access.%20There%20have%20been%20multiple%20instances%20of%20PLA%20troops%20kidnapping%20Indian%20citizens%20on%20Indian%20soil.%20In%202022%2C%20a%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20himself%20alleged%20that%20the%20PLA%20had%20abducted%20and%20tortured%2019-year-old%20Miram%20Taron%20for%20ten%20days.%20During%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Itanagar%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRahulGandhi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%40RahulGandhi%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20met%20the%20family%20of%20Tapor%20Pullom%2C%20who%20has%20been%20missing%20since%20he%20was%20allegedly%20abducted%20by%20the%20PLA%20in%202015.%20Modiji%2C%20bhul%20gaye%20kya%3F%20Were%20you%20lying%20to%20the%20people%20back%20then%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E2.%20Manipur%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20virtual%20civil%20war%20for%20nearly%20a%20year%20now.%20Hundreds%20of%20people%20have%20died%20in%20widespread%20violence%2C%20lakhs%20have%20been%20displaced%2C%20communities%20are%20at%20war%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20the%20administration%20has%20collapsed.%20The%20violence%20continues%20%E2%80%93%20two%20youth%20in%20Moreh%20were%20beaten%20up%20on%20the%207th%20of%20March%2C%20and%20Junior%20Commissioned%20Officer%20(JCO)%20Konsam%20Kheda%20Singh%20of%20the%20Indian%20Army%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20his%20own%20house%20in%20Thoubal%20district%20by%20militants%20on%20the%208th%20of%20March.%20Why%20has%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20ordinarily%20misusing%20taxpayer%E2%80%99s%20money%20to%20campaign%20around%20the%20country%2C%20not%20found%20the%20time%20to%20visit%20Manipur%20yet%2C%20or%20even%20take%20a%20call%20with%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20the%20political%20parties%20of%20the%20state%3F%20Is%20he%20waiting%20for%20the%20people%20of%20India%20to%20buy%20him%20a%20ticket%20to%20Imphal%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E3.%20The%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Organization%20(ENPO)%20has%20declared%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20emergency%E2%80%9D%20in%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20%E2%80%94%20threatening%20to%20disallow%20any%20political%20party%20from%20campaigning%20or%20contesting%20elections%20in%20the%20region%20%E2%80%94%20to%20protest%20the%20delay%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98Frontier%20Nagaland%20Territory.%E2%80%99%20The%20Konyak%20Union%20(KU)%20and%20Tikhir%20Tribal%20Council%20(TTC)%20have%20echoed%20the%20ENPO%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20of%20a%20public%20emergency.%20On%20the%208th%20of%20March%2C%20there%20was%20a%20large-scale%20bandh%20in%20most%20of%20Eastern%20Nagaland.%20Even%20as%20the%20situation%20becomes%20increasingly%20more%20tense%20and%20threatens%20to%20disrupt%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20democracy%20in%20Nagaland%2C%20the%20Union%20Government%20appears%20to%20be%20missing%20in%20action.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20new%20development%3A%20we%20have%20seen%20the%20Modi%20Sarkar%20previously%20obscure%20the%20political%20situation%20of%20Nagaland%20with%20the%202015%20Naga%20Accord%2C%20which%20has%20not%20even%20been%20released%20to%20the%20public%2C%20much%20less%20implemented.%20What%20steps%20is%20the%20Modi%20Sarkar%20taking%20to%20defuse%20the%20situation%20brewing%20in%20eastern%20Nagaland%20today%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E4.%20Three%20labourers%20working%20in%20a%20stone%20quarry%20in%20Cachar%2C%20Assam%20in%20December%202023%20were%20abducted%20by%20the%20Zeliangrong%20United%20Front%20(ZUF).%20In%20mid-February%202024%2C%2010%20labourers%20working%20at%20Finboro%20Coalmine%20in%20Changlang%20district%20on%20the%20Assam-Arunachal%20Pradesh%20border%20were%20abducted%20by%20the%20National%20Socialist%20Council%20of%20Nagaland%20(NSCN)%20and%20the%20United%20Liberation%20Front%20of%20Assam%20Independent%20(ULFA-I).%20There%20has%20been%20a%20disturbing%20re-emergence%20of%20separatist%20groups%20emboldened%20to%20disrupt%20the%20lives%20of%20common%20people%20and%20enact%20their%20reign%20of%20terror.%20When%20faced%20with%20this%20renewed%20violence%2C%20why%20is%20the%20Modi%20Sarkar%20sitting%20on%20its%20hands%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709982756000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09151958%2FGINULmyWEAAyNn9.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-in-kaziranga-congress-poses-four-questions-on-security-situation-in-northeast%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20border%20with%20China%2C%20Manipur%2C%20Nagaland%2C%20and%20Cachar%20in%20Assam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-in-kaziranga-congress-poses-four-questions-on-security-situation-in-northeast%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Winnie%20the%20Pooh%20slasher%20movie%20named%20worst%20film%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709982221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF633%2Fproduction%2F_132872036_069b07ec-7333-4c99-a716-f8a1a4abcc59.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-68510904%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20horror%20film%20won%20five%20awards%20at%20the%20ceremony%20described%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bugly%20cousin%20to%20the%20Oscars%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%