0a%20warrant%20and%20must%20be%20turned%20over%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%2C%20where%20they%20will%20face%20charges%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20Section%20224%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2077%20Myanmar%20nationals%20slated%20for%20deportation%2C%2055%20are%20reported%20to%20be%20women%2C%20five%20are%20children%2C%20and%20the%20remainder%20are%20adult%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20these%20developments%2C%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20took%20to%20Facebook%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20batch%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20who%20entered%20India%20illegally%20deported%20today.%20Although%20India%20is%20not%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%201951%20Refugee%20Convention%2C%20it%20has%20given%20shelter%20%26amp%3B%20aid%20to%20those%20fleeing%20the%20crisis%20in%20Myanmar%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%20with%20a%20systematic%20approach.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20border%20fencing%20to%20control%20the%20influx%20of%20Myanmar%20nationals%20into%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1709980418000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F09155959%2Fimage-1932.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffirst-batch-of-seven-myanmar-nationals-deported-from-india-77-more-to-follow-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20will%20be%20transported%20by%20helicopters%20to%20Moreh%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20Myanmar%20officials%20at%20Tamu%2C%20Imphal%20Free%20Press%20reported.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ffirst-batch-of-seven-myanmar-nationals-deported-from-india-77-more-to-follow-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Olive%20oil%20most%20stolen%20item%20in%20Spanish%20supermarkets%20as%20gangs%20target%20'liquid%20gold'%22