retiring%20in%20October%202023%2C%20the%20outgoing%20police%20chief%20of%20Indian-administered%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Dilbag%20Singh%2C%20asserted%20that%20the%20Himalayan%20region%2C%20over%20which%20Pakistan%20also%20claims%20sovereignty%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Ccoming%20out%20of%20the%20dark%20era%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%20Yet%20over%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20events%20conspired%20to%20prove%20him%20wrong.%20Militants%20carried%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fhead-constable-police-shot-killed-terrorists-north-jammu-kashmir-wailoo-kralpora-2456274-2023-10-31%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20separate%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20killing%20two%20police%20officers%20and%20a%20migrant%20labourer%2C%20in%20three%20different%20districts%20of%20the%20Kashmir%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20substantial%20gap%20between%20the%20Indian%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20become%20%E2%80%9Cpeaceful%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20reality%20in%20the%20restive%20region.%20The%20government%E2%80%99s%20narrative%20contains%20more%20than%20a%20bit%20of%20wishful%20thinking%3A%20security%20in%20the%20area%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20supreme%20importance%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20set%20his%20cap%20on%20consolidating%20control%20and%20wiping%20out%20armed%20militancy%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EOn%20August%205%2C%202019%2C%20the%20freshly%20re-elected%20Modi%20administration%20broke%20with%2070%20years%20of%20Indian%20constitutional%20tradition%20by%20overhauling%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20administrative%20order.%20It%20revoked%20Article%20370%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20had%20guaranteed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20Muslim-majority%20state%20semi-autonomy%20since%20it%20joined%20the%20Indian%20Union%20in%201947.%20According%20to%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20was%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vox.com%2Fworld%2F2019%2F8%2F9%2F20798273%2Fkashmir-narendra-modi-india-speech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20hurdle%20for%20development%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20wellspring%20of%20%E2%80%9Cseparatism%2C%20nepotism%20and%20corruption%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Modi%20administration%20then%20split%20the%20state%20into%20two%20%E2%80%9Cunion%20territories%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20one%20called%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20the%20other%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%93%20placing%20them%20both%20under%20direct%20Central%20government%20control%2C%20via%20appointed%20lieutenant%20governors.%20Officials%20promised%20that%20these%20decisions%2C%20none%20of%20which%20were%20taken%20in%20consultation%20with%20the%20local%20population%20or%20political%20representatives%2C%20would%20bring%20%E2%80%9Cpeace%20and%20prosperity%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20region%20after%20three%20decades%20of%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08160332%2FH20220203107835.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08160332%2FH20220203107835.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08160332%2FH20220203107835-300x153.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08160332%2FH20220203107835-1024x523.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-684118%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22613%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20in%20Nowshera%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20File%20image.%20Photo%3A%20PIB%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EFour%20and%20half%20years%20down%20the%20road%20from%20this%20momentous%20decision%2C%20there%20have%20been%20improvements%20in%20the%20security%20situation%2C%20but%20the%20changes%20have%20not%20been%20the%20panacea%20that%20was%20promised.%20While%2C%20according%20to%20official%20data%2C%20the%20number%20of%20militants%20is%20low%20compared%20to%20the%20past%2C%20not%20a%20week%20goes%20by%20without%20an%20insurgent%20attack%20or%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Fkashmir-india-pakistan-rebels-army-738f00207eee974a23360e0c09f8625f%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeadly%20encounter%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0between%20insurgents%20and%20security%20forces.%20Kashmiri%20youth%2C%20disgruntled%20with%20New%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20policy%20of%20direct%20control%20of%20the%20region%20and%20deprived%20of%20political%20space%20to%20vent%20their%20frustration%2C%20continue%20to%20join%20militant%20groups.%20Lacking%20proper%20training%20and%20weapons%2C%20many%20of%20these%20new%20recruits%20are%20killed%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20months%2C%20if%20not%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20security%20officials%2C%20militants%20could%20ramp%20up%20their%20activity%20if%20they%20choose%20%E2%80%93%20or%20if%20Pakistan%20chooses%2C%20since%20Islamabad%20has%20historically%20supported%20the%20anti-India%20insurgency%20that%20has%20cost%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives%20since%20the%20late%201980s.%20Islamabad%20backed%20the%20separatist%20insurrection%20that%20erupted%20in%201989%2C%20and%20over%20the%20years%20it%20has%20provided%20funds%2C%20training%20and%20equipment%20to%20various%20militant%20outfits%2C%20even%20if%20the%20assistance%20seems%20to%20have%20tailed%20off%20since%20the%20two%20countries%20recommitted%20to%20a%20ceasefire%20along%20the%20contested%20border%20in%202021.%20But%20however%20Pakistan%E2%80%99