%5C%22%3Ehybrid%20militants%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20authorities%20note%20that%20these%20insurgents%20have%20a%20radicalisation%20agenda.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20militants%E2%80%99%20thinking%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20when%20they%20go%20after%20soft%20targets%2C%20the%20reaction%20from%20the%20state%20will%20be%20disproportionate%20%E2%80%93%20we%20will%20pick%20up%20people%2C%20question%20them%2C%20harass%20them%20%E2%80%A6%20which%20will%20create%20more%20disaffection%20among%20people%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20mid-level%20police%20officer%20explained.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20what%20they%20want%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwed-high-hopes-of-meeting-the-pm-say-kashmiris-who-werent-allowed-to-enter-the-stadium%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%E2%80%99d%20High%20Hopes%20of%20Meeting%20the%20PM%2C%E2%80%99%20Say%20Kashmiris%20Who%20Weren%E2%80%99t%20Allowed%20to%20Enter%20the%20Stadium%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20systematically%20downplays%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20violence%2C%20instead%20showcasing%20its%20claims%20of%20peace%20and%20stability%20in%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20acknowledge%20their%20presence%E2%80%9D%2C%20Omar%20Abdullah%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20state%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20from%202009%20to%202015%2C%20observed%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20militants.%20But%20the%20facts%20speak%20for%20themselves.%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2F2023-a-year-of-ironies-and-paradoxes-in-jk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOfficial%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0shows%20that%20the%20security%20forces%20killed%20113%20militants%2C%20arrested%20500%20of%20their%20associates%20and%20busted%20up%2089%20militant%20cells%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202023%3B%2034%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20as%20well.%20Tensions%20in%20Kashmir%20became%20hard%20to%20cover%20up%20in%202023%20when%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20which%20held%20the%20presidency%20of%20the%20G20%2C%20organised%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20bloc%E2%80%99s%20Tourism%20Working%20Group%20in%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20summer%20capital%2C%20Srinagar.%20Usually%20prohibited%20from%20visiting%20the%20region%2C%20foreign%20journalists%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbc.ca%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fkashmir-g20-tourism-meeting-india-1.6854073%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscovered%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Kashmiris%20live%20in%20fear%20and%20resent%20the%20central%20government.%20When%20the%20journalists%20asked%20about%20heavy-handed%20security%20measures%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20they%20received%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fscribes-tough-questions-during-g20-meet-spurs-union-minister-to-question-their-mindset%2Fcid%2F1938916%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20angry%20response%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20a%20central%20government%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResentment%20of%20the%20Indian%20State%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20constitutional%20changes%20undertaken%20in%202019%2C%20alongside%20the%20more%20than%20half%20a%20million%20soldiers%20now%20stationed%20in%20the%20region%2C%20have%20bred%20deep%20public%20discontent.%20In%20the%20eyes%20of%20many%20Kashmiris%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20turned%20Kashmir%20into%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpolice%20state%E2%80%9D%20where%20arbitrary%20detentions%2C%20high%20levels%20of%20incarceration%20and%20constant%20surveillance%20have%20generated%20a%20climate%20of%20pervasive%20fear.%20But%20the%20disaffection%20with%20central%20rule%20extends%20much%20further%20than%20criticism%20of%20the%20massive%20army%20presence.%20The%20scrapping%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20under%20Article%20370%20had%20already%20annulled%20the%20exclusive%20rights%20that%20locally%20born%20people%20had%20over%20land%20ownership%20and%20government%20jobs%2C%20but%20a%20series%20of%20laws%20ushered%20in%20by%20the%20central%20government%20since%20then%20have%20sown%20further%20resentment.%20New%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fnow-outsiders-can-buy-land-in-jammu-and-kashmir%2Farticle61713541.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eland%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnc-pdp-reject-jk-domicile-law%2Farticle31622785.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edomicile%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0laws%20have%20allowed%20Indians%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20to%20purchase%20land%2C%20acquire%20residency%20and%20apply%20for%20government%20jobs%20in%20the%20territory%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ECumulatively%2C%20these%20changes%20have%20triggered%20fears%20that%20the%20central%20government%2C%20which%20is%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nationalist%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20is%20pushing%20for%20demographic%20change%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20Muslim-majority%20region.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20civilisational%20project%E2%80%9D%2C%20says%20former%20minister%20Akhtar%2C%20summing%20up%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.crisisgroup.org%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Fkashmir%2F310-raising-stakes-jammu-and-kashmir%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperception%20of%20many%20Kashmiris%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20see%20us%20as%20an%20anomaly%20on%20the%20map%20of%20Hindu%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20has%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-apni-party-delegation-meets-home-minister-amit-shah%2Farticle61667110.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisclaimed%20such%20intentions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20the%20view%20that%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Hindu%20nationalist%20government%20is%20intent%20on%20disempowering%20local%20Muslims%20is%20now%20an%20article%20of%20faith%20throughout%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20civil%20society%20and%20political%20establishment.%20Most%20political%20leaders%20point%20out%20that%20none%20of%20the%20top%20administrators%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20police%20officers%20appointed%20by%20New%20Delhi%20are%20locals.%20%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20of%20them%20represent%20the%20majority%20community%3F%20How%20many%20speak%20the%20local%20language%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20control%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20%5BHindu%5D%20majoritarianism.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20want%20local%20officers%20to%20get%20their%20due%20space%E2%80%9D%2C%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Abdullah%20lamented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20political%20life%20has%20all%20but%20come%20to%20a%20standstill.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-local-body-representatives-in-jk-from-january-9-no-assembly-since-2018%2Farticle67716327.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elast%20regional%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0took%20place%20in%202014%2C%20and%20the%20elected%20government%20ceased%20to%20exist%20in%202018%20after%20New%20Delhi%20imposed%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%2C%20a%20constitutional%20device%20that%20places%20regional%20authorities%20under%20central%20government%20control.%20Addressing%20Kashmiris%20in%202019%2C%20two%20days%20after%20announcing%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20new%20union%20territories%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3