ondon-europe-road-trip%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20relocated%20to%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20upon%20completing%20his%20graduation%20and%20commenced%20employment%20at%20a%20renowned%20firm.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20five%20years%20of%20working%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20corporate%20finance%20didn%E2%80%99t%20resonate%20with%20me.%20It%20lacked%20the%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20I%20sought.%20Despite%20the%20arduous%20journey%20to%20secure%20such%20a%20position%20%E2%80%94%20navigating%20academic%20challenges%2C%20seeking%20out%20the%20right%20institutions%2C%20and%20cultivating%20the%20necessary%20connections%2C%20the%20work%20became%20somewhat%20mundane.%20While%20the%20field%20suits%20many%2C%20I%20yearned%20for%20something%20more%20tangible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamit%20then%20decided%20to%20return%20to%20India.%20%E2%80%9CUpon%20my%20return%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20at%20a%20crossroads%20with%20no%20clear%20direction.%20It%20felt%20like%20starting%20anew.%20I%20opted%20to%20take%20some%20time%20off%20and%20embark%20on%20a%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Fbw7USCmL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3Fbw7USCmL%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C