20the%20age%20of%2045%20that%20Uma%20revived%20her%20interest%20in%20painting.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20started%20to%20paint%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20reborn.%20Then%2C%20I%20saw%20a%20documentary%20on%20coral%20reefs%20which%20encouraged%20me%20to%20read%20more%20about%20them.%20I%20started%20painting%20them%20and%20holding%20exhibitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20while%20speaking%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20pollution%20on%20coral%20reefs%2C%20she%20was%20mocked%20by%20one%20of%20her%20cousins.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20had%20seen%20coral%20reefs%20in%20real%20life%2C%20or%20how%20the%20ocean%20even%20looked%20underwater%2C%20or%20what%20the%20colour%20of%20the%20ocean%20was.%20Although%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20blue%20and%20beautiful%20outside%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20full%20of%20pollution%20inside.%20This%20sparked%20my%20curiosity%20to%20dive%20deep%20into%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Uma%20took%20up%20swimming%20to%20become%20a%20diver.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20family%20supported%20me%20in%20this%20decision.%20The%20same%20year%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20to%20celebrate%20our%2025th%20wedding%20anniversary.%20As%20a%20present%2C%20my%20son%20paid%20for%20my%20certification%20course%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20learn%20to%20dive.%20I%20advised%20myself%20to%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20as%20it%20hardly%20comes%20to%20anyone%20at%20this%20age%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Uma%20dived%20in%20deep%2C%20she%20was%20taken%20aback%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F190080%2Felephant-underwater-pictures-lacadive-diving-school-sumer-verma-photographer-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderwater%20beauty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20surreal%20world.%20When%20the%20water%20envelopes%20your%20body%2C%20you%20forget%20about%20the%20outside%20world%20and%20the%20w