3EGoing%20beyond%20wildlife%2C%20Karamjeet%20has%20also%20captured%20spectacular%20photos%20of%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20landscape%2C%20its%20tribes%20and%20night%20skies.%20As%20Karamjeet%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLadakh%20contains%20an%20amazing%20range%20of%20wildlife%2C%20including%20birds%20and%20mammals.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20shame%20not%20many%20people%20notice%20these%20incredible%20creatures.%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%20awestruck%20by%20the%20beauty%20around%20us%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20capture%20it%20with%20my%20camera.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20his%20Nikon%20D750%20with%20a%20200-500%20mm%20lens%20which%20his%20father%20got%20him%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20a%20lot%20of%20persisting%E2%80%9D%2C%20here%E2%80%99s%20Karamjeet%E2%80%99s%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC3XivjHxCmf%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campai