%206%2C000%20composting%20kits%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20and%20Karnataka.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20the%20composter%20work%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavani%E2%80%99s%20home%20composting%20kit%20can%20handle%20up%20to%201%20kg%20of%20organic%20waste%20daily.%20Suitable%20for%20balconies%2C%20the%20portable%20composter%20can%20be%20kept%20anywhere%20just%20like%20a%20dustbin.%20Priced%20at%20Rs%203%2C500%2C%20the%20food%20waste%20composter%20comes%20along%20with%20a%20green%20mix%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20composter%20works%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20kit%20comprises%20a%20rotating%20composter%20and%202%20kg%20pack%20of%20green%20mix%20powder.%20To%20the%20composter%2C%20add%20a%20complete%20pack%20of%20green%20mix%20powder%2C%20add%20400%20ml%20of%20water%20on%20day%201%2C%20and%20mix%20it%20with%20your%20hand.%20You%20can%20add%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F195317%2Flifestyle-compost-bucket-home-kitchen-waste-organic-garden-diy-order-online%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20any%20kind%2C%20including%20fruit%20peels%2C%20leftover%20rice%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20to%20the%20composter.%20Once%20you%20add%20the%20waste%2C%20close%20the%20lid%20and%20rotate%2Fspin%20the%20composter%20five%20times.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPavani%20mentions%20that%20her%20composter%20has%20the%20edge%20over%20traditional%20methods%20of%20composting.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20the%20process%20of%20composting%20takes%2045-60%20days%20but%20with%20this%2C%20we%20can%20prepare%20compost%20in%20just%20seven%20days.%20We%20do%20not%20increase%20the%20temperature%20of%20the%20composter%20artificially%2C%20it%20is%20a%20natural%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-inst